summary: My attempt at making a passable female highelf/altmer.
descriptionHtml:
My attempt at making a passable female highelf/altmer. 

Safe is at the beginning of the Game in Helgen Keep (unbinded hands) after entering & fighting with Ralof. Modifications can be done via the console \" ~ \" key and typing \".showracemenu\".

I used various mods cause the elf-races are so butt-ugly by default ...
In addition I used human eyes & eycolors for the highelf-race (selected DarkBlue, Brown & Green from HQ Eyes & renamed it to eyehighelf.dds, eyehighelfdarkyellow.dds & eyehighelforange.dds)

required/recommended mods: (also available via disc-icon(required files))

Detailed Bodies
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=256
